net.proteusframework.core

Interface CoercionView<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Attributes<K>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FunctionBasedCoercionView, MapAttributes

    public interface CoercionView<K>
    A view of data indexed by a key that can optionally be coerced from one type to another.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
